title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 4 Evening' game
title_page: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 4 Evening' game
maintext:
BALTIMORE (AP) _ The winning numbers in Wednesday evening’s drawing of the Maryland Lottery’s “Pick 4 Evening” game were:
4-3-9-3
(four, three, nine, three)
